headline: Comcast Completes Network Expansions to Residents and Businesses in Spokane County
summary: SPOKANE, Wash., February 09, 2026--Comcast today announced that it has completed the expansion of its network in three underserved areas of Spokane County. These projects bring reliable, high-speed, symmetrical Internet from America’s smartest and most reliable converged network to more than 2,200 homes and businesses in Chattaroy, Four Lakes, and Medical Lake.
